---
title: Roast Pumpkin Ravioloni & Creamy Bacon Sauce with Tomato Bruschetta & Cucumber Salad
description: Has there been a pasta as flavour-packed as this one? The star of the show has to be the creamy bacon and leek sauce,
enveloping the pumpkin ravioloni in a warm embrace. Finish this picture-perfect dinner with a side of tomato bruschetta and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese - now dig in and gobble it all down!

*We’ve replaced the basil in this recipe with parsley due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
